---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
	title="Join the Waitlist | Learn with Dorell" 
	description="Join the waitlist for Dorell's AI Automation cohort and be the first to know when the next cohort opens."
	keywords="AI automation, waitlist, cohort learning, ChatGPT automation, n8n workflows"
	ogImage="/og-learn-with-dorell.png"
>
	<div class="min-h-screen flex flex-col">
		<!-- Simple, elegant header -->
		<header class="py-8 border-b border-gray-100">
			<div class="container mx-auto px-4">
				<div class="flex justify-between items-center">
					<a href="/" class="flex items-center gap-3 hover:opacity-90 transition-opacity">
						<img src="/logo.png" alt="Learn with Dorell" class="w-10 h-10">
						<span class="font-medium text-xl">Learn with Dorell</span>
					</a>
					<a href="/" class="text-indigo-600 hover:text-indigo-800 font-medium">
						‚Üê Back to homepage
					</a>
				</div>
			</div>
		</header>
		
		<main class="flex-grow">
			<!-- Waitlist section with embedded n8n form -->
			<section class="py-16 md:py-24">
				<div class="container mx-auto px-4 max-w-2xl">
					<h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight mb-8 leading-tight text-center">
						Join the <span class="text-indigo-600">Waitlist</span>
					</h1>
					
					<p class="text-xl text-gray-600 mb-12 text-center">
						Be the first to know when the next AI Automation cohort opens...
					</p>
					
					<div class="mb-12">
						<!-- n8n Embedded Form -->
						<iframe
							src="https://n8n.dorellworks.com/form/a767362f-3ea6-4f67-8451-f7dfd10e8625"
							frameborder="0"
							width="100%"
							height="100%"
							style="min-height: 870px; border-radius: 0.5rem;"
						></iframe>

						 
					</div>
					
					<div class="text-center text-gray-600">
						<p>By joining the waitlist, you'll receive priority access to the next cohort before it's announced publicly.</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</section>
		</main>
		
		<!-- Simple footer -->
		<footer class="py-8 border-t border-gray-100">
			<div class="container mx-auto px-4 text-center text-gray-500">
				<p>No pressure. Just real stuff ‚Äî with heart, with purpose.</p>
				<p class="mt-4">Made with <span class="text-purple-600">üíú</span> by <a href="https://dorelljames.com" class="text-indigo-600 hover:text-indigo-800 underline">Dorell</a> &middot; <a href="https://github.com/dorelljames/lwd-astro" class="text-indigo-600 hover:text-indigo-800 underline">Source</a></p>
			</div>
		</footer>
	</div>
</Layout> 